# pylangdetect

Lightweight language detection (rule-based + ML hybrid).

## Installation

```bash
pip install pylangdetect
```

## Usage

```python
from pylangdetect import detect_language, is_english

detect_language("Hello world")  # "en"
is_english("Hello world")  # True
```

